## Additional Resources

### Videos
[What on Earth is Recursion](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv9NEXX1VHc)


```
factorial(n)= n*factorial
factorial```


```
int factorial (int n)
//recursive version
{
  if (n == 1) return 1;
  else
  return n*factorial(n-1)1;
}
```

```
<recursion>

factorial 1
  i am the number 1.
factorial 2
  wants factorial 1?
factorial 3
  wants factorial 2?
factorial 4
  wants factorial 3?
main program 
  wants factorial 4? = 24
```

In the pending multipliers each one was holding onto a different value of `n`.


